 integral equations. We also present techniques to\nstabilize the solution at low frequencies, and impose a Calder\\'{o}n\npreconditioner. Several results presented serve to validate the proposed\napproach as well as demonstrate some of its capabilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2015 19:18:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-22"}
