s\nat large $k$ values ($\\ge 0.5 \\,{\\rm Mpc}^{-1}$), and a weak correlation\nbetween the smallest and largest $k$ values. There is also a small\nanti-correlation between the errors in the smallest and intermediate $k$\nvalues. These results are relevant for the $k$ range that will be probed by the\ncurrent and upcoming EoR 21-cm experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2015 20:04:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Oct 2015 18:54:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2015 11:20:26 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 27 Nov 2015 05:51:20 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 31 Dec 2015 06:56:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-26"}
