able budget allocation\nin each step, we develop a 1/(15e)-competitive algorithm. This setting extends\nthe secretary problem, and its variant, the submodular knapsack secretary\nproblem. Notably, our algorithm improves over the best known approximation for\nthe latter problem, even though it applies to a more general setting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2015 13:06:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2016 21:14:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Mar 2018 17:10:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-13"}
